[[cdo:3 nguŏk 17 hô̤ (nùng-lĭk)]] [[zh-min-nan:3 goe̍h 17 ji̍t (kū-le̍k)]] [[zh-yue:三月十七]] {{Lunisolar March}} '''March 17''' is the 17th day of the month {{ill|March (Lunisolar)|ja|3月 (旧暦)|lt=March|12=draft}}, the 3rd month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Senshō|ja|先勝|12=draft}}.
== Events == * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|12=draft}} 11th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦}} [[1513]] {{ill|April 22|ja|4月22日}}) – {{ill|Toyotachi Dōsetsu|ja|立花道雪}}, a military commander, was born (died [[1585]] {{Sfn|楠戸|2009|p=165}}).
* {{ill|Kansei|ja|寛政|12=draft}} 9th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} [[1797]] {{ill|April 13|ja|4月13日}}) – {{ill|Ōhara Yūgaku|ja|大原幽学}}, an agricultural policy scholar, was born (died [[1858]]). * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} [[1870]] {{ill|April 17|ja|4月17日}}) – {{ill|Mitanmura Tobiyu|ja|三田村鳶魚}}, an essayist and historian, was born (died [[1952]]). * 明治3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} 1870, {{ill|April 17|ja|4月17日}}) – {{ill|Yanaguchi Naoma|ja|谷口尚真}}, a military officer, was born (died [[1941]]).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Taika|ja|大化|12=draft}} 5th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦}} [[649]] {{ill|May 3|ja|5月3日}}) – {{ill|Abenai Maro|ja|阿倍内麻呂}}, a noble from the Asuka period (birth year unknown). * [[Daidō]] 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦}} [[806]] {{ill|April 9|ja|4月9日}}) – {{ill|Emperor Kanmu|ja|桓武天皇}}, the 50th Emperor of Japan (born [[737]]). * {{ill|Ōhō|ja|応保}} 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦}} [[1162]] {{ill|May 2|ja|5月2日}}) – {{ill|Taira Motomori|ja|平基盛}}, a military commander of the Taira clan (born [[1139]]).
