{{Lunisolar March|qq=}} '''March 17''' is the 17th day of the month {{ill|March (Lunisolar)|ja|3月 (旧暦)|lt=March (Yayoi)|qq=}}, the 3rd month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=}} day is {{ill|Senshō|ja|先勝|qq=}}.
== Events == * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=}} 11th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} [[1513]] {{ill|April 22|ja|4月22日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Toyotachi Dōsetsu|ja|立花道雪|qq=}}, a military commander, was born (died [[1585]] {{Sfn|楠戸|2009|p=165|qq=}}).
* {{ill|Kansei|ja|寛政|qq=}} 9th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1797]] {{ill|April 13|ja|4月13日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Ōhara Yūgaku|ja|大原幽学|qq=}}, an agricultural policy scholar, was born (died [[1858]]). * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1870]] {{ill|April 17|ja|4月17日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Mitanmura Tobiyu|ja|三田村鳶魚|qq=}}, an essayist and historian, was born (died [[1952]]). * 明治3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} 1870, {{ill|April 17|ja|4月17日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Yanaguchi Naoma|ja|谷口尚真|qq=}}, a military officer, was born (died [[1941]]).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Taika|ja|大化|qq=}} 5th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} [[649]] {{ill|May 3|ja|5月3日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Abenai Maro|ja|阿倍内麻呂|qq=}}, a noble from the Asuka period (birth year unknown). * [[Daidō]] 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} [[806]] {{ill|April 9|ja|4月9日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Emperor Kanmu|ja|桓武天皇|qq=}}, the 50th Emperor of Japan (born [[737]]). * {{ill|Ōhō|ja|応保|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} [[1162]] {{ill|May 2|ja|5月2日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Taira Motomori|ja|平基盛|qq=}}, a military commander of the Taira clan (born [[1139]]).
