== Events == * [[:en:Tenshō (Momoyama period)|Tenshō Era]] 11th year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[1513]] [[:en:April 22|April 22]]) – [[:en:Tachibana Dōsetsu|Toyotachi Dōsetsu]], a military commander, was born (died [[1585]] {{Sfn|楠戸|2009|p=165|qq=}}).
* [[:en:Kansei|Kansei]] 9th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1797]] [[:en:April 13|April 13]]) – [[:en:Ōhara Yūgaku|Ōhara Yūgaku]], an agricultural policy scholar, was born (died [[1858]]). * [[:en:Meiji era|Meiji era]] 3rd year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1870]] [[:en:April 17|April 17]]) – {{ill|Mitanmura Tobiyu|ja|三田村鳶魚|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mitanmura Tobiyu|qq=}}, an essayist and historian, was born (died [[1952]]). * 明治3rd year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] 1870, [[:en:April 17|April 17]]) – {{ill|Yanaguchi Naoma|ja|谷口尚真|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yanaguchi Naoma|qq=}}, a military officer, was born (died [[1941]]).
== Deaths == * [[:en:Taika (era)|Taika]] 5th year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[649]] [[:en:May 3|May 3]]) – {{ill|Abenai Maro|ja|阿倍内麻呂|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Abenai Maro|qq=}}, a noble from the Asuka period (birth year unknown). * [[Daidō]] 1st year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[806]] [[:en:April 9|April 9]]) – [[:en:Emperor Kanmu|Emperor Kanmu]], the 50th Emperor of Japan (born [[737]]). * [[:en:Ōhō|Ōhō]] 2nd year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[1162]] [[:en:May 2|May 2]]) – {{ill|Taira Motomori|ja|平基盛|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Taira Motomori|qq=}}, a military commander of the Taira clan (born [[1139]]).
